summary:
- **Substantial Holder Ceasing**: Macquarie Group Limited (MQG) and its controlled entities have ceased to be substantial holders in Helia Group Limited (HLI.AX).  
- **Key Changes**:  
  - **17-Jun-25**: MIMGL sold 933 shares at AUD 5.36 (on-market).  
  - **17-Jun-25**: MBL returned borrowed shares (31,000) and collateral (41,657).  
  - **18-Jun-25**: MISL executed mixed on-market trades (buy/sell) at prices between AUD 5.34–5.38.  
  - **18-Jun-25**: MBL borrowed 237,696 shares and returned 487,953 collateral shares.  

**No material impacts on valuation, liquidity, or capital structure identified.**  
*(Note: Detailed annexures list minor trades and legal agreements, but no aggregate position changes or material disclosures.)*
